    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ群：891791828</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demo已经上线，欢迎试玩！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/6d680d645bd3340a90e962afb345fe07.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黑夜轮回》是一款肉鸽卡牌+战棋游戏。玩家需要在每次Roguelike冒险中逐步构建自己的卡组，在战棋棋盘上击败从史莱姆到吸血鬼的各种强大敌人。快攻、OTK、控制流……各色卡组都能扭转战局，杀出重围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在战斗中会同时控制三名角色，从而实现战棋游戏独有的前后排、包夹、卡位、相互掩护等有趣操作。得益于创新性的元素暴击机制，任意三名角色都可以有20+种套路供玩家选择，小combo更是不计其数！玩家会在涌现式的自由度中，收获前所未有的创造乐趣与爽快体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来这座小镇，亲手终结黑夜的轮回，让晨光重现大地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/600c0623d45f79e24232aa5e3a340b3f.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=107 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在每场战斗中同时控制三名角色，可以让他们互有分工——有人负责前排抗伤害，有人负责后排猛输出，有人负责侧翼搞偷袭……在丰富有趣的地图上，凭借角色们的特性、发挥套牌的长处、灵活运用场地中的各种元素，以战略智慧谋取胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/6f887c6b6fa186d3ba177ea3acb67cde.poster.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/6f887c6b6fa186d3ba177ea3acb67cde.webm?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/6f887c6b6fa186d3ba177ea3acb67cde.mp4?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/e4d619f2732b078ef146c3663b7e29d2.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中可以利用火水草三元素循环克制的暴击机制，轻松打出成吨的伤害。三人小队如何精妙配合打出元素暴击、如何灵活站位防止敌人打出元素暴击……双方的博弈如同顶级棋手对弈，一切都要仔细规划，又要根据局势随机应变！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/01557ae412b0880f1a4fdde1f9da8bd3.poster.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/01557ae412b0880f1a4fdde1f9da8bd3.webm?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/01557ae412b0880f1a4fdde1f9da8bd3.mp4?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/7a599d134538fb16233e0d0ee93ad65e.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=89 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每名角色都有特色天赋与大量职业卡牌。300+张卡牌搭配100+种装备与物品，使任意三名角色都能组出20+种套路供玩家选择。三色循环？一拳超人？连环突刺？炸弹爆破？天降凤凰？连场地里的土墙都有好几种办法变废为宝！在这里，用你的创造力尽情蹂躏敌人吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/46089b62255880a6b7e6b73f501a4776.poster.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/46089b62255880a6b7e6b73f501a4776.webm?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/46089b62255880a6b7e6b73f501a4776.mp4?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/78c758f54e6b6aad802edeab7140a64d.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=118 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局游戏都是一次全新的体验，多样的地图、事件、战斗和奇遇等待着玩家的探索。从村外溪流开始，在危险中一步步穿越村庄，直到登上隐藏着秘密的城堡！在一次次冒险中，逐渐解锁更多内容与新角色。还有难度超高的进阶挑战，等待不畏艰险的玩家来逐一征服！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/95a92b029d7176ab4d7da494c5c4524b.poster.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/95a92b029d7176ab4d7da494c5c4524b.webm?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/95a92b029d7176ab4d7da494c5c4524b.mp4?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/775aa0e6cd8388e9f97821376b14008a.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为何黑夜会轮回？为何元素生物们入侵了村庄？每名主角与BOSS，都在为了什么而战？玩家可以收集轮回碎片，从回忆中了解往事。还可以完成一系列OTK挑战关卡，解锁角色的专属卡牌、装备与事件。等集齐了所有回忆碎片后，玩家就能看穿潜藏在黑夜之中的真相，彻底解开轮回的谜团！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/e09c8beb1fe532e8a10298b25adae4cc.poster.avif?t=1769585740\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/e09c8beb1fe532e8a10298b25adae4cc.webm?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372240/extras/e09c8beb1fe532e8a10298b25adae4cc.mp4?t=1769585740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
